<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Service Platform</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Google Fonts -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@700&family=Lora:wght@400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* General Styles */
        body {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-family: 'Lora', serif;
            background-color: #F5F5F5; /* Background Color */
            color: #0D1B2A; /* Text Color */
            line-height: 1.75;
        }

        /* Navbar */
        .navbar-brand {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            color: #c89f18 !important; /* Accent Color */
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .navbar-brand:hover {
            color: #1F3B4D !important; /* Primary Color */
        }
        .nav-item .nav-link {
            color: #0D1B2A !important; /* Text Color */
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            padding: 8px 20px;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .nav-item .nav-link:hover {
            color: #D4AF37 !important; /* Accent Color */
        }
        .dropdown-item{
            color: #c89f18;
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero-section {
            background: #1F3B4D; /* Primary Color */
            color: #F5F5F5; /* Background Color */
            padding: 120px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .hero-section h1 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #D4AF37; /* Accent Color */
        }
        .hero-section p {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        /* Cards Section */
        .card-container {
            padding: 80px 0;
            background-color: #F5F5F5; /* Background Color */
        }
        .card {
            background-color: #FFFFFF;
            border: 1px solid #A0A7B1; /* Secondary Color */
            border-radius: 12px;
            color: #0D1B2A; /* Text Color */
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0px 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
        .card-title {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1F3B4D; /* Primary Color */
        }
        .btn-primary {
            background: #D4AF37; /* Accent Color */
            border: none;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            border-radius: 30px;
            padding: 10px 25px;
            transition: background 0.3s ease;
        }
        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: #A0A7B1; /* Secondary Color */
        }

        /* About, Testimonials, Contact, Footer */
        .about-section, .testimonial-section, .contact-section {
            padding: 100px 0;
        }
        .testimonial {
            padding: 25px;
            background: #FFFFFF;
            border: 1px solid #D4AF37; /* Accent Color */
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0px 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .testimonial h5 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1F3B4D; /* Primary Color */
        }
        .testimonial img {
            width: 70px;
            height: 70px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-right: 15px;
        }

        /* Contact Form */
        .contact-form input, .contact-form textarea {
            background-color: #F5F5F5;
            color: #0D1B2A;
            border: 1px solid #A0A7B1;
            padding: 14px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
        .contact-form button {
            background: #D4AF37; /* Accent Color */
            color: #FFFFFF;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            border-radius: 30px;
            padding: 12px 35px;
            transition: background 0.3s ease;
        }
        .contact-form button:hover {
            background: #A0A7B1; /* Secondary Color */
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            background: #1F3B4D; /* Primary Color */
            color: #F5F5F5;
            padding: 30px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        /* Header Section */
        .about-header {
            background-color: #1F3B4D;
            padding: 80px 0;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }

        .about-header h1 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            color: #D4AF37;
        }

        /* Team Section */
        .team-section {
            padding: 50px 0;
        }

        .team-member {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .team-member:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .team-member img {
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            object-fit: cover;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .team-member h3 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: #1F3B4D;
        }

        .team-member p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #6c757d;
            max-width: 250px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .team-member .role {
            color: #D4AF37;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }


    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Navbar -->
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg">
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Brand -->
        <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">Epic Engineers</a>

        <!-- Toggler button for mobile view -->
        <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav" aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
            <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
        </button>

        <!-- Collapsible Navbar -->
        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
            <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
                <!-- Login Dropdown -->
                <li class="nav-item dropdown">
                    <a class="nav-link dropdown-toggle" href="#" id="loginDropdown" role="button" data-bs-toggle="dropdown" aria-expanded="false">Login</a>
                    <ul class="dropdown-menu">
                        <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="/user/login">User</a></li>
                        <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="/services/login">Service Provider</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <!-- Signup Dropdown -->
                <li class="nav-item dropdown">
                    <a class="nav-link dropdown-toggle" href="#" id="signupDropdown" role="button" data-bs-toggle="dropdown" aria-expanded="false">Signup</a>
                    <ul class="dropdown-menu">
                        <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="/user/signup">User</a></li>
                        <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="/services/signup">Service Provider</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</nav>


    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Welcome to Our Services Platform</h1>
            <p>Connecting you with the best service providers in your area, with unmatched expertise and luxury.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Cards Section -->
    <section class="card-container">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card p-4">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Plumbing Services</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Professional plumbing services for all your needs, available 24/7.</p>
                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Learn More</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card p-4">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Electrical Services</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Experienced electricians ready to handle your electrical needs.</p>
                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Learn More</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card p-4">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Cleaning Services</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Top-notch cleaning services for both residential and commercial properties.</p>
                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Learn More</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <!-- About Us Header -->
    <section class="about-header">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>About Our Project Team</h1>
            <p>Meet the dedicated team members of our college project, working together to innovate and create.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Team Section -->
    <section class="team-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row justify-content-center">
                <!-- Team Member 1 -->
                <div class="col-md-3">
