                        <p>Robert focuses on server-side logic, ensuring the functionality behind the project works seamlessly.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Team Member 4 -->
                <div class="col-md-3">
                    <div class="team-member">
                        <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/deohfzmmp/image/upload/v1729364306/Mini_Project/tmp-1-1729364301438.jpg" alt="Team Member 4">
